seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: After killing off all of humanity, Food attempts to create their own utopia.

episodes.name: First Course
episodes.overview: The great Food Fight has ended. Food reigns victorious over humanity. They’re free to create their own Foodtopia. But not everything is as it seems…

episodes.name: Second Course
episodes.overview: Frank, Brenda and Barry embark on a mission to save food hostages before they ALL DIE!! Sammy fills his hole with a new art form: Stand up comedy. But not all is as it seems…

episodes.name: Third Course
episodes.overview: Food pride is high. They decide to throw a Burning Man Festival. Frank and Brenda have to hide a secret from Barry. Unfortunately, nothing is as it seems…

episodes.name: Fourth Course
episodes.overview: A new currency forms a class system in Foodtopia. Frank and Brenda set out to fix it. Though, not everything is as it seems…

episodes.name: Fifth Course
episodes.overview: A Machiavellian orange, Julius, gains popularity in Foodtopia. Frank and Brenda struggle to maintain control. But not all is as it seems…

episodes.name: Sixth Course
episodes.overview: Election day is upon Foodtopia: Julius versus Frank and Brenda. But relationship trouble threatens their chances. And not all is as it seems…

episodes.name: Seventh Course
episodes.overview: Brenda sets out to find the good in the dictator orange, Julius. Frank ties up some loose ends. And nothing is as it seems…

episodes.name: Eight Course
episodes.overview: Barry and Sammy have to clear Frank's name and save Foodtopia! Julius must be stopped! But not all is as it seems to be...
